Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.36,0:00:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情提要\N{\fs12}Previously on The Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,塔利克  把枪\N{\fs12}Taliek put the gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我在代表塔利克·艾伦\N{\fs12}I'm representing Taliek Allen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,上诉\N{\fs12}in his appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦想要剥夺塔利克·艾伦的生命\N{\fs12}The Commonwealth wants to take Taliek Allen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡不是随便就能发给谁的东西\N{\fs12}Death is not something to be handed out arbitrarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在告诉我  你在拉选票解雇我儿子吗\N{\fs12}Are you telling me that you are trying to round up enough votes to fire my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天不会改选票的\N{\fs12}I'm not changing my vote today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是把尼克投票出局了  把我也投出去吧\N{\fs12}You vote Nick out, you vote me out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都无所谓了\N{\fs12}It doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沃尔特  嘿  我是尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Walter. Hey, it's Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得现在是时候一起坐下来谈谈工作了\N{\fs12}l think it's time we sat down and talked about working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,明天怎么样\N{\fs12}How about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好  可以  谢谢  沃尔特  拜拜\N{\fs12}Great. Great. Thanks, Walter. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对  是  我马上到\N{\fs12}Right. Yeah, l'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  医生说了什么\N{\fs12}Hey. What did the doctor say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他想做剖腹产\N{\fs12}He wants to preform a C-section.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的心跳不规律\N{\fs12}The baby's heartbeat's irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的有必要吗  露露  你才35周\N{\fs12}ls it really necessary? Lulu, you're 35 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,医生在担心  尼克\N{\fs12}The doctor's concerned, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感受到心脏的跳动\N{\fs12}l'm spotting and the heart rate is fluctuating,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是不能再等了\N{\fs12}and he just doesn't want to wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  你不用做你不想做的事\N{\fs12}Lulu. you don't have to do anything that you don't want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道  但是我害怕  尼克\N{\fs12}l know, l know. But l'm scared, Nick,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想孩子出什么事\N{\fs12}and l don't want anything to happen to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,该走了  亲\N{\fs12}lt's time to go, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你来吗\N{\fs12}Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生吗  我是布雷姆医生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin? Dr. Brem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我治疗过很多唐氏综合症的孩子  所以如果你有任何问题\N{\fs12}l work with a lot of  Down Syndrome babies, so if you have any questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们检查了她的心脏  超声波看起来挺好的\N{\fs12}We checked her heart. The echocardiogram looked good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她的新生儿评分也正常  只是出生体重会有点低\N{\fs12}Her APGARs are normal. She's just low birth weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们会等到她五磅的时候再让她离开早产保温箱\N{\fs12}So we'll leave her in the isolette until she gets up to five pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要待多久\N{\fs12}How long will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,三到四天\N{\fs12}Three or four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个健康的女宝宝  法林先生  恭喜\N{\fs12}She's a healthy baby girl, Mr. Fallin. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么样了\N{\fs12}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs12}She's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有哭\N{\fs12}ls she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没有  她睡着了\N{\fs12}No. No. She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有说我什么时候能抱她了吗\N{\fs12}When did they say that l can hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,医生说她三到四天就能出来了\N{\fs12}The doctor said that she could come out in three or four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想抱抱她  - 我知道  我知道\N{\fs12}- l want to hold her. - l know. l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是真的想\N{\fs12}No, l really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  工作上发生什么了吗\N{\fs12}What--what happened with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我被解雇了\N{\fs12}l got fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天晚点和沃尔特·麦克尼尔有个会\N{\fs12}l have a meeting with Walter McNeil later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让我加入他的事务所\N{\fs12}He wants me to join his firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我  你能帮我个忙吗\N{\fs12}You know, l... Could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,LSP的资金申请书  我忘在我桌上了\N{\fs12}LSP funding application. l left it on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就把它给  呃  阿尔文\N{\fs12}Just give it to, uh, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他会议在周五\N{\fs12}Tell him that meeting is Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的累了\N{\fs12}l'm really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜  她叫什么名字\N{\fs12}Congratulations. What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我们还没有想好\N{\fs12}Uh, we don't really have one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她  呃  她来得有点  早了\N{\fs12}She, uh, she came kinda... early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这很棒  你们会收获很多乐趣的\N{\fs12}That's wonderful. You guys are gonna have so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你没什么机会来这儿接案子了\N{\fs12}Uh, you're not here by any chance to take a case or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为阿尔文在他办公室里有点自闭\N{\fs12}Because Alvin has kind of shut himself in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有点\N{\fs12}Kind of?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他把自己关在办公室里\N{\fs12}He has shut himself in his office,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道在这里做什么\N{\fs12}and l kind of have no idea what l'm doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我在弗兰克尔法官面前要做个拘留听证会\N{\fs12}l have this detention hearing in front of Judge Frankel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么建议吗\N{\fs12}Any advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克尔吗  对  直接说重点\N{\fs12}Frankel? Yeah. Get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要试着去打动他  因为他不在乎\N{\fs12}Don't try to pull on his heartstrings because he doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  - 嘿  恭喜\N{\fs12}- Alvin. - Hey. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是个女孩  很好啊\N{\fs12}A baby girl. Terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,露露想让我给你些提醒关于这次\N{\fs12}Lulu wanted me to remind you about the meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,州财政委员会的会议\N{\fs12}with the State Funding Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 脑额叶损伤  - 什么\N{\fs12}- Frontal lobe damage. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚  在最高法院拒绝审理塔里克的案子后\N{\fs12}Last night, after the Supreme Court refused to hear Taliek's case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去翻遍了他的档案  想找点什么\N{\fs12}l went back over his files looking for something, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,脑额叶损伤吗\N{\fs12}Frontal lobe damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去年用卸胎棒袭击的  - 对\N{\fs12}- The attack last year with a tire iron. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,主治医生做了个大脑皮层创伤的标记\N{\fs12}The treating doctor made a notation that there was trauma to the cerebral cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他的公辩律师从没为他辩护过\N{\fs12}His public defender never entered it into his defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有脑损伤的话就不能被处死\N{\fs12}You can't be put to death if you have brain damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  阿尔文  我刚告诉露露我会来的\N{\fs12}Well, Alvin, l just told Lulu l'd stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是想确认你没有忘记\N{\fs12}She just wanted to make sure that you remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,和董事会的资金会议\N{\fs12}the meeting with the Funding Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我把这个资料搬到会议室吗\N{\fs12}Would you help me move this stum into the meeting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,格雷琴告诉我你回来了\N{\fs12}Gretchen told me you were back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  你取名字了吗\N{\fs12}Oh, do you have a name yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  恭喜你  儿子\N{\fs12}Well, congratulations, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你和麦克尼尔开会了\N{\fs12}l heard you had a meeting with McNeil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,传得真快\N{\fs12}Word travels fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是真的了  是吧\N{\fs12}So it's true, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克尼尔\N{\fs12}McNeil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直觉得他有点滑头  但\N{\fs12}l always thought he was a little slick, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他挺好的  挺好的\N{\fs12}Well, he's fine. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  儿子  我有关于  呃\N{\fs12}Listen, son, l have about, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一笔三百万的生意  我可以把他过渡给你\N{\fs12}3 million in business that l could transition over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要辞职了吗  - 好吧  我已经71岁了  儿子\N{\fs12}- You're stepping down? - Well, l'm T1 years old, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是合伙人怎么办\N{\fs12}But what about the partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  对我来说  我一点也不在乎那些合伙人\N{\fs12}Well, as far as l'm concerned, l don't give a damn about the partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那  你需要帮忙处理这些垃圾吗  - 不  我明白了\N{\fs12}- So, you need help with this crap? - No, l got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我可以找个人把你剩下的东西送过去\N{\fs12}You know, l could get a messenger to send over the rest of your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  嘿\N{\fs12}Nick. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fs12}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
