Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好  不错  不错\N{\fs12}Yeah. Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  尼克  我就是\N{\fs12}Well, gosh, Nick, l'm just...
