Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要飞到智利才能到南极\N{\fs12}You gotta fly to Chile to get to the South Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
