Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  你可以把我从这里弄出去吗\N{\fs12}Oh, you can get me out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我想我们可以让你活下去\N{\fs12}Well, l think we can keep you alive.
