Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  变化很大啊\N{\fs12}Wow, it's so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
