Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一年五万一千美元\N{\fs12}How does _51 ,OOO a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有公司信用卡  你自己付停车费  每周按小时计费  听起来怎么样\N{\fs12}no corporate credit cards, pay your own parking, and 70-hour weeks sound?
