Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个工作吗\N{\fs12}This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
