Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的  不错\N{\fs12}Fine. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要用你自己的话阐述犯罪的细节\N{\fs12}You need to, in your own words, state the details of the crime
