Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不  塔里克  那样说没用\N{\fs12}No, Taliek, that's just not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我应该说什么 呵\N{\fs12}What am l supposed to say, huh?
