Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还没盖棺定论\N{\fs12}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我会记住在最后的时刻你试着帮助过我\N{\fs12}You know, l remember the last time you tried to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心不在这儿  哪怕只是一点  然后我们输了\N{\fs12}Your heart wasn't in it, not even a little, and we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你对它毫不在乎\N{\fs12}Yeah, you didn't give a damn about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧  你就只是说说说\N{\fs12}See, you just talked and talked and talked,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是脑子里什么都没有想\N{\fs12}but there was nothing happening behind your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的话来说  为什么你要请求宽恕\N{\fs12}ln your words, why should your plea for mercy be granted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想我死吗  - 不  我不想\N{\fs12}- You want me to die? - No, l don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 这和我没关系  塔里克\N{\fs12}- Why? - It's not about me, Taliek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有了  因为你是要我的生命而战斗的人\N{\fs12}lt is now, since you're the one who's gotta fight for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  为什么你不花点时间来想想关于宽恕的问题呢\N{\fs12}You know, why don't you just take a little time and think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我没有太多时间了  你知道的  对我而言\N{\fs12}Look, l don't have much, you know, for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这一件事  伙计\N{\fs12}Except for one thing, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的骄傲\N{\fs12}That's my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果你不觉得我们可以做这件事  现在就告诉我\N{\fs12}So if you don't think we can do this thing, just tell me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是浪费你和我的时间\N{\fs12}instead of wasting your time and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,做一些你不想做的事\N{\fs12}doing something you don't want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话  你不认为我们能成功\N{\fs12}Be honest. You don't think we can win this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你有非常小的机会  好吗\N{\fs12}You have very little chance, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  用你的话说\N{\fs12}So, in your words--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那又有什么意义呢  伙计  你为什么\N{\fs12}Then what's the point, man! Why are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  我准备走了\N{\fs12}Hey, l'm ready to roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人说服我接受这件事\N{\fs12}You guys talked me into taking this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我想要两千七百万  而你让我接受两千四百万\N{\fs12}l mean, l wanted 27 million, and you talked me into taking 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我就损失了三百万  现在是这意思么  你在开玩笑吗\N{\fs12}So, l'm out three million there. And now this? You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,按照惯例  卖方必须支付所有环境清理的费用\N{\fs12}lt is customary for the seller to pay for any environmental clean-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是两万两千美元\N{\fs12}lt's _22,OOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,买家对这个态度很坚决\N{\fs12}The buyer's adamant about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那卖方也是如此\N{\fs12}So is the seller.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下  法林先生\N{\fs12}Excuse me. Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  但是有一位马斯特森先生正在等您\N{\fs12}l am so sorry, but there's a Mr. Masterson waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他说是生死攸关的情况\N{\fs12}He says it's literally a life or death situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,两分钟\N{\fs12}Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你同意条款  然后我这里  那些是条款\N{\fs12}You agree to terms. And in my book, those are the terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  一旦你同意了条款  你就不能再改了\N{\fs12}l mean, once you've agreed to the terms, you can't just change the terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,法院拒绝了我们的请求\N{\fs12}The courts denied our claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们有给任何理由吗  - 他们不需要给\N{\fs12}- Did they give any reason? - They don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找了塔里克  他把我解雇了\N{\fs12}l went to tell Taliek. He fired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你告诉他没必要再试了\N{\fs12}He says you told him there's no point in trying any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  我不是这么说的  - 你到底说了什么\N{\fs12}- No, that's not what l said. - What the hell did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你想我试着帮那个家伙\N{\fs12}Alvin, you wanted me to try and help the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我按你说的做了\N{\fs12}l did what you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他炒了他的律师  然后  你知道  我们能做什么吗\N{\fs12}lf he fires his lawyers, then, you know, what can l do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对  好\N{\fs12}Right. Well--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我有个会才开了一半\N{\fs12}You know, l'm in the middle of a meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  现在只剩下一个赦免委员会的审讯了\N{\fs12}Well, the thing is all that's left is a Board of Pardons hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一个犯人不能自己辩护  所以如果他不用我们的话  他就要死了\N{\fs12}A prisoner can't represent himself. So if he doesn't use us, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是好吧  回去开你的会吧\N{\fs12}But please, go back to your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过那个狗娘养的菲尔普斯了  我要两千四百万  就是这样\N{\fs12}l told that son of a bitch Phelps l would take the 24 million, but that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在讨价还价了  我的意思很清楚了\N{\fs12}No nickel and diming from signing to closing. And l meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再花一分钱了\N{\fs12}l'm not shelling out another penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我会打电话给菲尔普斯\N{\fs12}All right. l'll call Phelps,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他您拒绝支付环境清理的费用\N{\fs12}tell him you refuse to pay for the environmental clean-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还要告诉他我不喜欢改变条款\N{\fs12}And tell him l don't appreciate the changing terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,生意不是这么做的\N{\fs12}That's no way to do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你来这真是太好了  尼克\N{\fs12}Hey. Really great to have you here, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么样了\N{\fs12}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她挺好的\N{\fs12}She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她醒了两三个小时\N{\fs12}She was wide awake for a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她用力捏我的手指\N{\fs12}She squeezed my finger really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那很棒\N{\fs12}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我把我的地址本忘在我办公室的桌子上了\N{\fs12}You know, l left my address book on my desk in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我拿一下吗\N{\fs12}Could you please get it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Sure. -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文告诉我你不打算回去工作\N{\fs12}Alvin told me you're not going back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对  不做全职了\N{\fs12}Yeah. Not full-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候决定的\N{\fs12}When did you decide that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天\N{\fs12}Yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要我\N{\fs12}She needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要我\N{\fs12}She needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我觉得你会做出正确的决定\N{\fs12}Well, l think you're making the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  那位女士从行政办公室来的\N{\fs12}So, the woman from the administrative office came by
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,带着出生证明\N{\fs12}with the birth certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有填\N{\fs12}l haven't filled it out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我会帮你填的\N{\fs12}Well, l could do that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  我想先和你谈一下\N{\fs12}No. l wanted to talk to you about it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想因为我有孩子的监护权\N{\fs12}l think that because l am gonna have physical custody
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  因为我们没有结婚\N{\fs12}and, uh... and because we're not married--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你想她用你的姓氏吗\N{\fs12}You want her to have your last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我  我是这么想的  对\N{\fs12}Yeah. l think--l think so, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我准备去看看她  那\N{\fs12}Well, l'm gonna go see her, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好  - 好\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这个想解放她自己的女孩的代表\N{\fs12}l'm representing this girl who wants to emancipate herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她还没有工作吗  - 不  还没有\N{\fs12}- Does she have a job yet? - No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  除非她有工作  否则你赢不了\N{\fs12}Well, unless she has a job, you won't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,南极  你什么时候去\N{\fs12}Antarctica. When are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去\N{\fs12}l'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么不去  - 我得工作\N{\fs12}- Why not? - l have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你错过了你的机会  总之\N{\fs12}Well, you've missed your window, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你什么意思  - 季节\N{\fs12}- What do you mean? - Seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在赤道以南  它们的季节相反  那儿下面太冷了\N{\fs12}South of the equator, they're the opposite. It's freezing down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你想去的话\N{\fs12}Even if you wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的同情心在哪儿  - 什么\N{\fs12}- Where's your compassion? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你的同情心  它在哪儿\N{\fs12}Your compassion. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天就拜托了你一件事  一件事\N{\fs12}l entrusted you to do one thing today. One thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助一个死刑犯  给他一点希望\N{\fs12}Help a condemned man. Give him a little hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么\N{\fs12}And what'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他问我他的机会是什么  阿尔文\N{\fs12}Well, he asked me what his chances are, Alvin,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我决定诚实的告诉他  我告诉了他真相\N{\fs12}so l decided to be honest with him. l told him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,塔里克·艾伦  七岁时\N{\fs12}Taliek Allen: Seven years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他的爸爸在塔里克看电视的时候朝自己的头开了枪\N{\fs12}His father shoots himself in the head while Taliek is watching television.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,塔里克·艾伦  十岁时  他的妈妈遗弃了他\N{\fs12}Taliek Allen: Ten years old. His mother abandons him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,塔里克·艾伦  十一岁时  贩毒卖可卡因被捕\N{\fs12}Taliek Allen: 1 1 years old. Arrested selling crack cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道这些故事  阿尔文  - 这些不只是故事  尼克\N{\fs12}- l know the stories, Alvin. - These aren't just stories, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一段人生\N{\fs12}This is a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我们一起多久了\N{\fs12}How long were you with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有清醒过\N{\fs12}Were you even awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  嘿  布拉德·富尔顿\N{\fs12}Nick! Hey! Brad Fulton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  是  我知道\N{\fs12}Uh, yeah, l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能帮忙克莱顿的案子\N{\fs12}Glad you're helping out in the Clayton matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  谢谢你\N{\fs12}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰是我的客户  我带他来的\N{\fs12}John's my client. l brought him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了让你更明白\N{\fs12}Just so you're real clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你的帮忙\N{\fs12}Glad you're helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我应该  呃  有时间去喝一杯\N{\fs12}You and l should, uh, go get a drink sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  呃  和菲尔普斯谈克莱顿的事吗\N{\fs12}Oh, uh, talk to Phelps on the Clayton matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还不用  - 克莱顿每小时都打电话来\N{\fs12}- Not yet. - Clayton's calling every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我去\N{\fs12}All right. l'll get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道这单只有两万两千  但是  我马上就做\N{\fs12}- l know it's only 22 grand, but-- - l'll do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,查·菲尔普斯  谢谢\N{\fs12}Chuck Phelps, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,查  嘿  尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Chuck, hey. Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  呃  我在麦克尼尔和约翰·克莱顿一起工作\N{\fs12}Listen, uh, l'm over at McNeil working with John Clayton.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对  你知道  我打电话来是为了清理费用\N{\fs12}Yeah. You know, l was calling about the clean-up costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  对  我完全理解\N{\fs12}Oh, yeah, l understand perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  呃\N{\fs12}But, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以各退一步\N{\fs12}Maybe we could meet somewhere in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,查克  我只是个传话人  查  查\N{\fs12}Chuck, l'm just the messenger. Chuck--Chuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好  高兴  呃  跟你聊也很高兴\N{\fs12}Yeah. Nice, uh-- Nice talking to you, too.
