Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.34,0:30:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到了\N{\fs12}l realized what that meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.86,0:30:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你想的太多了  尼克\N{\fs12}l think you're reading too much into it, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.80,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不觉得我想多了  露露\N{\fs12}No, l don't think l am, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.88,0:30:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让孩子用你的姓氏  因为\N{\fs12}You want the baby to have your last name because...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.68,0:30:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你不想要我的\N{\fs12}because you don't want to have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.13,0:31:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我说得对吗\N{\fs12}Am l right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.60,0:31:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,露露\N{\fs12}Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.48,0:31:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.78,0:31:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs12}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.06,0:31:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很想这么做  尼克\N{\fs12}l really wanted to make this work, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.52,0:31:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我\N{\fs12}You know, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.56,0:31:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但就是有些事  呃  就是有些事\N{\fs12}But there's just something, um, just something--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.78,0:31:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  你不用告诉我\N{\fs12}lt's okay. You don't have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.96,0:31:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的感觉\N{\fs12}lt's just how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.64,0:31:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对  就是我的感觉\N{\fs12}Yeah, it's just how l feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.48,0:31:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.60,0:31:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给她你的姓氏\N{\fs12}Give her your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.70,0:31:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这不会改变我对她的感觉\N{\fs12}lt's not gonna change the way l feel about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.04,0:31:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.04,0:31:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  我去看她了\N{\fs12}Well, l'm gonna go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.38,0:32:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.14,0:32:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  过来看你的孙女\N{\fs12}Dad. Come and see your granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.66,0:32:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  好\N{\fs12}Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.44,0:32:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}She's beautiful, Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.98,0:32:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  这会\N{\fs12}You know, it's gonna be--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.96,0:32:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,会很艰难  我知道  我知道\N{\fs12}lt's gonna be hard. l know. l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.93,0:32:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.59,0:32:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她真漂亮\N{\fs12}She is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.96,0:32:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.33,0:32:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天退休了\N{\fs12}l stepped down today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.40,0:32:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,退了律师顾问吗\N{\fs12}Of counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.93,0:32:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.56,0:32:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我有很长的时间  陪着她了\N{\fs12}So l'm gonna have a lot of time... to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.72,0:32:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好啊\N{\fs12}That'll be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.80,0:33:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想如果我们每周日都在一起吃晚饭可能会更好\N{\fs12}l was thinking it might be nice if we had Sunday dinner every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.06,0:33:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.54,0:33:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我  露露还有她\N{\fs12}You and me and Lulu and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.78,0:33:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.74,0:33:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对  那会很棒的\N{\fs12}Yeah, that'll be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.86,0:33:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.94,0:33:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.69,0:34:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.10,0:34:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有消息吗  - 不  还没有\N{\fs12}- Any news? - No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.63,0:34:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.03,0:34:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是在想你可能想去吃点东西\N{\fs12}l just thought you might want to go get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等电话\N{\fs12}l gotta wait for the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.69,0:34:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.39,0:34:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好明天的融资会议了吗\N{\fs12}You ready for the funding meeting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.46,0:34:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.74,0:34:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那\N{\fs12}That.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.86,0:34:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想把把这个地方和儿童项目结合起来\N{\fs12}Been thinking about merging this place with the Children's Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.30,0:34:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凯特·肖的地方吗  - 对\N{\fs12}- Kate Shaw's place? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.26,0:34:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我只剩这些时间了  尼克\N{\fs12}l've only got so much time left, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.40,0:34:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大半辈子都在这里\N{\fs12}l've given this place most of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.26,0:34:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事情要做在我  你知道  继续前进\N{\fs12}l got things to do before l, you know... move On.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.40,0:34:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\fs12}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.24,0:34:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我的手指开始麻木了  有刺痛感\N{\fs12}Well, my fingers get numb, tingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.16,0:34:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时会摔倒\N{\fs12}l fall down sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.34,0:34:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.60,0:34:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道它要来了\N{\fs12}l knew it was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.28,0:34:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是  呃  没那么吓人\N{\fs12}lt's just, uh-- It's not as scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.78,0:34:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是发生了\N{\fs12}That it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.16,0:35:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  如果你听有消息了  打我电话\N{\fs12}Well, if you hear, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.30,0:35:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮\N{\fs12}Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.72,0:35:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好名字\N{\fs12}lt's a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.44,0:35:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.06,0:35:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.43,0:35:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是艾尔文\N{\fs12}lt's Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.66,0:35:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.14,0:36:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,法庭拒绝了我们的请愿书\N{\fs12}The courts rejected our petitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.86,0:36:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没告诉他吗\N{\fs12}Did you tell him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.40,0:36:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你应该告诉他了\N{\fs12}Well, you should tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.14,0:36:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我最后的案子\N{\fs12}He's my last case.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.68,0:36:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在说什么  - 我是这么想的\N{\fs12}- What are you talking about? - l think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.82,0:36:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢  别这样  阿尔文  - 不  不是因为我们输了\N{\fs12}- Oh, come on, Alvin. - No, It's not because we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.68,0:36:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是时候做些别的事了\N{\fs12}lt's time for me to do some other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.74,0:36:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你能替我告诉他吗\N{\fs12}Would you tell him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.36,0:36:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可以  当然\N{\fs12}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.34,0:36:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.60,0:36:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你比你想象中的要好\N{\fs12}You're a better man than you think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.34,0:36:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.36,0:36:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,记住这点\N{\fs12}Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.96,0:36:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.42,0:36:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧  - 没事\N{\fs12}- Are you all right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.20,0:36:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.24,0:36:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,情绪上来了\N{\fs12}Emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.20,0:36:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.44,0:37:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早\N{\fs12}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.79,0:37:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,早\N{\fs12}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.44,0:37:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.96,0:40:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还要喝点什么吗\N{\fs12}Can l get you anything else to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.59,0:40:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再来杯咖啡或者水什么的\N{\fs12}Another comee or water or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.68,0:40:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.30,0:40:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.32,0:40:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  尼克\N{\fs12}Excuse me. Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.54,0:40:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道阿尔文在哪儿吗  - 他不在这儿吗\N{\fs12}- Do you know where Alvin is? - He's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.36,0:40:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他留了这个便条  去南极了\N{\fs12}No. He left this note: ''Gone to Antarctica.''
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.04,0:40:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很奇怪  不是吗  - 不\N{\fs12}- It's weird, isn't it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.32,0:40:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  州财政委员会的人在等我\N{\fs12}Well, l've got the people from the State Funding Board waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.32,0:41:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好  - 我不知道跟他们说什么\N{\fs12}- Right. - l don't know what to say to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.08,0:41:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉延迟了\N{\fs12}l'm sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.78,0:41:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文是来还是不来\N{\fs12}ls Alvin coming or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.22,0:41:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不  阿尔文不来参加这次会议了\N{\fs12}No. Alvin won't be coming to this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.38,0:41:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  不  别  我在这儿  我可以和你们谈\N{\fs12}No, no, no, please. l'm here. l'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.73,0:41:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fs12}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.30,0:41:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是尼克·法林\N{\fs12}My name's Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.00,0:41:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这儿的主管吗\N{\fs12}Are you in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.09,0:41:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对  是的  我是\N{\fs12}Yes. Yes, l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.62,0:41:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候开始的  - 开始  呃  好吧  我刚上任\N{\fs12}- Since when? - Since, uh-- Well, l just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.80,0:41:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你想坐下吗  请吧\N{\fs12}Would you like to take a seat, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.46,0:41:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  法尔林先生\N{\fs12}So, Mr. Fallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.72,0:41:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是法林\N{\fs12}Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.08,0:41:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  你需要什么\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, what are your needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.68,0:41:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,钱  很多钱\N{\fs12}Money...and a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.10,0:41:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有超过五千个客户  如果我们不仔细的话\N{\fs12}We have over 5,OOO clients here,and if we're not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.60,0:41:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们中的大多数人会走上法律体系的歧途\N{\fs12}most of them will wind up on the wrong end of the legal system.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.52,0:42:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们中的那些人还不知道\N{\fs12}Those of you that don't already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.08,0:42:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,匹兹堡法律服务的使命很简单\N{\fs12}the mission of Legal Services of Pittsburgh is simple:
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.30,0:42:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为儿童和贫困人民提供\N{\fs12}To provide quality legal representation
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.34,0:42:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有质量的合法的法律援助和辩护\N{\fs12}and advocacy assistance to children and to the indigent.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.02,0:42:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去年的年度预算超了一百万美金\N{\fs12}Our annual budget last year was a little over a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.44,0:42:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望你们今年能至少支付一半的费用\N{\fs12}We are hoping that this year you will pay for at least half of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.40,0:42:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦预算的削减迫使我们来寻找新的资金来源\N{\fs12}Federal budget cuts are forcing us to find new sources of funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.68,0:42:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们每增加一百美元就能创造一个不同的世界\N{\fs12}A 100/o increase on your part would make a world of dimerence.
